		<td><b>FCEUX to PowerMappers savestate converter</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />How difficult would it be to write a program that can convert savestate files from FCE Ultra/FCEUX into the format used by <a href="http://kkfos.aspekt.fi/projects/nes/powerpak/powermappers" class="postlink">PowerMappers</a> for the PowerPak?<br /><br />There are some savestates that I created with an emulator and I'd like to use them on the PowerPak now.<br /><br />So, is the data in these savestate files simple, so that a conversion would be a relatively mundane task? Or is it really complicated?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


