	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Compatibility might depend on the timing in a frame when savestates are taken by the emulator vs powermappers, but if this is not a problem the conversion itself would be very simple.<br /><br />Reverse engineering the savestate formats might take you some time, but FCEUX is open source, at least.

		

